          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For many, summer is a season of possibilities. For us, the opportunity to be a part of your happiest moments, and that’s the motto that drives our daily inspiration. Paez is for everyone passionate about life, who's looking for authentic experiences, who want to feel the world surrounding them, and who leave a positive footprint wherever they go.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
