      "blocks": {
        "caption_Mg7AJJ": {
          "type": "caption",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "We walk the talk to make you feel relaxed, to inspire you to take the moment and go for it, and to remind you of better days. Our values are:",
            "text_style": "subtitle",
            "text_size": "medium"
          }
        },
        "template--16679014564085__687d5820-bc5f-4aee-a372-45ad429690f6-16746394964eafefde-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "CREATIVITY",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "template--16679014564085__687d5820-bc5f-4aee-a372-45ad429690f6-16746394964eafefde-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We transform simple, comfortable and accessible products into fun, iconic and inspiring experiences</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "f1375db4-a3de-4186-bad3-1da57a05fa6b": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "RESPONSIBILITY",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "64b32af2-55ea-448d-96b3-3afe3e3ecf39": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We’re not alone in this planet, dude. We’re committed to do better for our community and planet by making choices that minimize the impact of our production</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "f217f862-fd18-45a9-992c-e6a4fdfec3d1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "LAID BACK",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "63c747a3-ca7d-4878-aedf-90f5b58c19ce": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We care about the after works, the weekends, the moments of leisure, your vacations. We want to be your absolute choice in those moments and the reminder of good times</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "fed68fe4-3dad-45d6-9377-b1c85552a395": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "JOY",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "3a286fcf-7d71-4a5b-8988-177b3d431d2c": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Good vibes all the way. We are optimistics! We believe we can work together on building a better world.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
