        "template--16679014564085__150135c6-339f-40f1-8b00-18c028fe6561-16746410352b1943ba-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We started our journey in Buenos Aires in 2006 when three friends united to spread good vibes, create innovative ideas, and share inspiring stories worldwide.<br/><br/>Since then, we’ve traveled to over 50 countries and made an impact while placing our Paez shoes on millions of feet. We’ve explored coastlines from east to west and north to south, always innovating.<br/><br/>Now based in Portugal, we proudly uphold our legacy with a colourful range of comfortable products. We believe in our vision: dreams come true and anything is possible.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
